parameters:
"You're right... This place seems safe, so let's take a
short break."\n<Yukine>\F[7]\AA[F]\FF[24]

(It's strange for us spirits to sweat. Not just Saku's body,
but here the boundary between the physical and the spiritual
becomes ambiguous.)\FF[41]\F[4]\AA[F]

(This bath seems clean. If I want to wash off sweat, this
might be a good place.)\F[1]

"Haa haa... It looks like we somehow managed to escape...
But what's going on? It's incredibly hot here. And I'm all
sticky from running."\n<Yukine>\F[11]

"It's as hot as the middle of summer just here. It must be
that time and space are strange in this place."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[23]
"Saku, just hang in there a little longer, okay?"\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[23]
(I wonder if there's anything useful here)

(Shampoo, conditioner, and soap. The shrine maiden said I
should be able to take a bath with these... I wonder if I
can do it right?)\F[5]

(This bath looks clean enough to use... But if I'm going to
take a bath, I need to find some soap.)\F[1]

(It seems like there's a child's spirit outside... What
could it be? They're very thin, and there are bruises all
over their body.)\F[5]

(Even the spirit has wounds remaining, what could have
happened? There shouldn't be any wounds remaining on a
soul.)\F[4]

"There's a child's spirit outside. They seem to want me to
open the door... but that child isn't coming any closer."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[20]
"...Aren't you going to let them in?"\n<Saku>\F[8]\AA[FF]\FF[24]
"...What should I do. Maybe I should let them in."\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[24]

\F[10](What should I do... But I have a bad feeling about this. Is
it really okay to open the door?)\AA[F]\FF[23]
(I have a bad feeling about this. I should stop for now)\F[10]
"Saku, just wait a little bit, okay?"\n<Yukine>\F[8]\AA[F]\FF[23]

\F[8](Let's look for something that might help that
child)\AA[F]\FF[23]
"Hey, you. Come on in, that place is--"\n<Yukine>\F[1]
"I'm hungry... This is delicious... It's so good"\n<The Boy Ghost>
"Onee-chan... Where did you go? Onee-chan... Onee--"\n<Saku>

\F[8](Let's look for something that might help that

"What's that... It looks really delicious."\n<The Boy Ghost>
"Can I eat it? I wonder if I'll get scolded..."\n<The Boy Ghost>

"You can eat it. It's your cake, so eat as much as you
want."\n<Yukine>\F[2]

"Ah, it was so sweet... I've never had anything this
delicious before... It really was tasty..."\n<The Boy Ghost>

"If only... I could have let you eat it while you were still
alive."\n<Yukine>\F[10]

"I'll let Saku eat too... But before that, we need to get
out of this world."\n<Yukine>\F[7]\AA[F]\FF[23]
"Yeah, that's right. Let's go outside together..."\n<Saku>\F[7]\AA[FF]\FF[23]

(But, it feels like there's still something left undone)

(The cord is torn and doesn't seem usable)
(There doesn't seem to be anything useful here)

(There's an old battery here. It might be useful for

(There are a lot of empty cans scattered around.)\F[8]

(There are cigarettes in the empty can. A strange smell is
coming from inside.)\F[8]

(It's an old kitchen. It's rusty and there are no signs of
it having been cleaned.)
(There are forks and spoons in the drawer.)
(All of them are still wrapped and unused.)

(It's an old stove. There are no signs of it being used for
cooking for a long time.)
(It's an old stove. Seems like only the kettle was used.)

(Is this a refrigerator? It's so stiff, I can't seem to open
it.)

(Is this a refrigerator? There's a big cake with
strawberries on it inside.)

(Trash is scattered around. There's a remote control lying
among it.)

"Damn... damn... why only me, I did nothing wrong. That's
for sure... damn, can't find my lighter"\n<Male Ghost>

"If he comes in here, he won't get away with it. If he
pisses me off again, I'll kill him."\n<Male Ghost>
(This is a machine called an air conditioner, right?)\F[5]
(This is a machine called an air conditioner, isn't it?)\F[5]
Press the button on the remote control
リモコンのボタンを押す
"Ah, cool air is coming out. It's still working."\n<Yukine>\F[5]
"Wow, what? There's wind blowing inside the house... why?"\n<Saku>\F[5]\AA[FF]\FF[28]
"I'll tell you once we go outside..."\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[28]
(I wonder if the room has cooled down now.)\n<Yukine>\F[1]\AA[F]\FF[28]
"Tch, it's always such a hassle."\n<Male Ghost>\F[1]\FF[28]\AA[N]

(The tree has been neglected. It's completely withered, I
wonder if it didn't get any water.)\F[5]

\F[5](There's a withered tree. Huh... there's something like a
paper inside the pot.)

Been married for four years, and life hasn't gotten any
better. It's all because of the debt my wife's father made.
Just because I became a co-signer, I'm the only one
suffering like this.

Today, the debt collectors came again. Can't they see by
looking at this house that there's no money? Of all things,
to borrow from a nasty loan shark. Damn it, the kid won't
stop crying and it's driving me nuts.

She ran away from home. Dumping that brat on me and
disappearing, what a joke. What am I supposed to do with
this stepchild? Doesn't warm up to me at all, and it's not
even my own kid.
Kept whining for mommy, so I hit her with the ashtray.

They found her. Seems like she committed suicide somewhere.
Her sister wants a funeral, but there's no money for that.

I was so irritated that I pressed a lit cigarette against
the kid and felt a bit better. Serves her right.

The debt collectors came again. Every single day, it's
driving me insane... I'll take out my frustrations by
beating up that brat. She's covered in purple bruises and
it's starting to look disgusting, maybe I'll try strangling
her with the TV cord.

The kid's gone blind. Looks like I hit her too much... Damn
it, I'm running out of cigarettes, and the kid's face isn't
fit to be seen outside anymore. Maybe I should just kick her
out.

It's so hot I can't go without the air conditioner. It
pisses me off that I have to hit the outside unit to keep it
running... That useless brat can't do it, so I have to. Got
so mad I kicked her in the face and she passed out with a
nosebleed.
Got blood on my pants, just great.

She's trembling and annoying, so I threw her outside. It's
too hot to bear without the air conditioner on, and then her
aunt comes bringing a birthday cake. Telling me to feed it
to the kid, what a joke.

If she endures a day outside, maybe I'll let her have some
cake.

The kid kicked the bucket. Just left her out in August and
she died. What a weakling, dying on her own like that. Shit,
is this really going to be pinned on me as murder?

Can't I just make it look like an accident? Come to think of
it, what was that kid's name again?
"This is awful... To do such things to a child."\n<Yukine>\F[15]
(I need to find a way to light the candle)

Let's call her over. It's a special birthday cake after
all... I have to celebrate for her.\F[1]
